Ye aapki taraf se matlab ki humne jab se mail dali hui hai bhi aise karke hua hai. Aapne us taraf se dali hai bhi dekho aap pata karo kisne dala hai ji ye sara kuch matlab ki.
Customer: [inaudible]
Executive: Haan.
Executive: Hmm. Theek hai ma'am, theek hai.
Customer: Theek hai.
